description:
Add a touch of simple elegance to your home decor with this wishbone-style chair from Hans Anderson Home. The unique design of this wood chair features sturdy beechwood construction that transforms a traditional look into a modern classic. The gracefully curving seat back and the gently sloping seat back combine with the supple cord-woven seat to deliver exceptional comfort.
